BitStreamReader = object
  src*: ptr UncheckedArray[uint8]
  len*, pos*: int
  when (defined(arm64) and defined(macosx)) or sizeof(int) == 4:
      bitBuffer*: uint32

  else:
      bitBuffer*: uint64

  bitsBuffered*: int
